title: Should He Pursue A Woman Who's In A Semi Open Relationship?
description:
He wants to hook up with a woman who is technically in an open relationship. The catch is that she only gets a "freebie" once a year. She wants him to be her "freebie", but he's morally conflicted. What should he do?
